    "description": "Are you an old sea dog and can't live a day without a light sea breeze?<br>Do you love the smell of napalm in the morning?<br>And your shooting accuracy and speed of reaction are legendary?<br><br>That’s why you here! Feel free to send present with 14 pounds of lead to bad guys and enjoy the results of your work with fireworks of planes burn like a red coal.<br>Now you can go wild! But remember that your ship must survive, otherwise not only the sea waves, but also the heavens may be behind your back.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Environment generation.<br></li><li>Arsenal includes 40mm AA cannons and RIM-7 missiles.<br></li><li>Progressively difficult levels with more enemies and higher aggression.<br></li><li>Different enemy planes: Attack aircraft, Fighter aircraft, Torpedo bomber and Bomber.<br></li><li>Perks to upgrade your ship and cannon.</li></ul>",
